          <source>The following example shows how to aid usability of a <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox&gt;</ph> by displaying an explanatory background image inside of the <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBox&gt;</ph> until the user inputs text, at which point the image is removed.</source>
